<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Olympic Games 2026</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>

<nav>
    <div class="logo">Olympics 2026</div>
    <div class="links">
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">Events</a>
        <a href="#">Athletes</a>
        <a href="#">Results</a>
    </div>
</nav>

<header class="hero">
    <div class="hero-box">
        <h1>Olympic Games 2026</h1>
        <p>The world’s biggest sporting event — unity, passion and records.</p>
        <button onclick="welcome()">Explore</button>
    </div>
</header>

<section class="section-title">
    <h2>Top Highlights</h2>
</section>

<section class="cards">

    <div class="card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521412644187-c49fa049e84d">
        <h3>Opening Ceremony</h3>
        <p>A global celebration of unity and sport.</p>
        <button onclick="story1()">Read More</button>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517649763962-0c623066013b">
        <h3>New Champions</h3>
        <p>Athletes break records and inspire millions.</p>
        <button onclick="story2()">Read More</button>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1461896836934-ffe607ba8211">
        <h3>Final Moments</h3>
        <p>Intense competitions decide the medals.</p>
        <button onclick="story3()">Read More</button>
    </div>

</section>

<section class="info">
    <h2>About the Olympic Games</h2>
    <p>
        The Olympic Games unite the world through sport, respect and excellence,
        creating unforgettable moments every edition.
    </p>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>Olympic Games 2026 • School Project</p>
</footer>

<script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>

